Former BBNaija housemate, Tolanibaj has said her relationship with Prince caused her embarrassment outside the house. Tolanibaj said this during the BBNaija reunion show on Monday night after Ebuka Obi-Uchendu asked her about her relationship with Prince. According to her, she stopped talking to Prince since November 2020 because all he did was to embarrass her. BBNaija Reunion: Why my relationship with Tolanibaj failed – Prince
“Prince made me look like I was desperate for his attention and relationship. “My relationship with him caused a lot of embarrassment from his family and the outside world. “I stopped talking to him in November and we can never be friends. Maybe cordial but not anytime soon.” BBNaija reunion: Tolanibaj assaults Vee, threatens her as conversation escalates